# Product Overview

**`product`** = sellable line (v2, PG). **`main`** = Mongo demo (v1, MongoDB).

| Edition        | Buyer     | Roles (this version)                       |
| -------------- | --------- | ------------------------------------------ |
| `personal`     | Collector | `owner`                                    |
| `professional` | Merchant  | `owner` (solo use; no customer logins yet) |

**Next version:** `customer` role for catalog / orders. **Not now:** `staff`, `guest`, `customer`.

**DB:** `POSTGRES_URL` only (ADR 004).

**Locale:** `zh-TW` \| `en` in deploy config; fixed at onboarding.

**Code:** `schemas/product/`, `models/product/`; domain **stock**.
